track_notes: You can start from La Brigue village where plenty car park. if you follow this track, you can short cut to activate only one summit. The descend from Chaberta looks difficult, just few rocks to unclimb.
This is the long way, for this small summit; park at the village de la Brigue, not far from the railway station.
This track is a variant. Park before the village, it is not difficult, the place is fine.
